Place face-api.min.js here for full offline support.

How to get it:
1) Download from jsDelivr (right-click -> Save link as):
   https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/face-api.js@0.22.2/dist/face-api.min.js
2) Save as: face-api.min.js (exact name) in this folder.

After adding the file:
- Reload the app once online so the Service Worker caches it.
- Then it will be available offline.
